msgid "AboutBodyLine1"
msgstr "Autofire Next is a .NET 10 and Avalonia rewrite of the original Python speedrunning controller tool."

msgid "AboutBodyLine2"
msgstr "This build now focuses on a controller-first dashboard, unified controller detection, profile persistence, logging, translations, and a reusable mapping engine."

msgid "AboutBodyLine3"
msgstr "Native controller providers are isolated behind interfaces so Windows, Linux, and macOS can grow independently."

msgid "AboutBodyLine4"
msgstr "The next editor pass should replace the raw JSON workflow with a dedicated per-control binding editor for buttons, sticks, triggers, touchpad actions, keyboard targets, and scripts."

